  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "The project willCatalyze economic transformation and job creation in key sectors.Improve the capabilities of SMEs, linking them with domestic and international partners (primarily India and China), leveraging the Nepali diaspora and improving access to finance to enable them to take promising ideas to scale and to strengthen their role in the economy.Work in collaboration with the private sector and the federal and provincial Government to improve sectoral constraints for SMEs.Generate evidence and learning on accelerating private sector development in low income countries like Nepal."
    },
